metadata.name: Surrender
metadata.description:
I surrender to the power of nature,
the waves of longing.
I surrender to the endless sky and dangerous storms.
Let the wind blow my soul away.
Let the stars light my path.
Let me be reborn this day.

Title: Surrender

Collection: Silence of the Soul

Location: Split, Croatia

Year taken: 2020

Dimension: 4888 x 3259

Medium : Photography

Edition: 1/1

About the Artist: Diana Junakovic is Croatian award winning photographer, Master of Arts and holder of AFIAP.
